## UML Workflow (Description)

[Start]
   ↓
Register Equipment → Store to Equipment Table
   ↓
Check Maintenance Required?
   ↓(Yes)                 ↓(No)
Supervisor Assigns Technician → END
   ↓
Technician Performs Maintenance 
   ↓
Update Maintenance Table
   ↓
Store Completed Record in Maintenance_History
   ↓
Generate Alerts if Deadline is Near
   ↓
Reports & BI Analysis
   ↓
[END]

## UML Activity Diagram Structure

 ┌───────────────────────────────┐
 │   Start                       │
 └──────────────┬────────────────┘
                ↓
 ┌───────────────────────────────┐
 │ Register Equipment            │
 └──────────────┬────────────────┘
                ↓
 ┌───────────────────────────────┐
 │ Is Maintenance Needed?        │◄─── Timer Event
 └───────┬─────────┬─────────────┘
         │Yes      │No
         ↓         ↓
 ┌───────────────────────────────┐
 │ Assign Technician             │
 └──────────────┬────────────────┘
                ↓
 ┌───────────────────────────────┐
 │ Technician Performs Task      │
 └──────────────┬────────────────┘
                ↓
 ┌───────────────────────────────┐
 │ Update Maintenance Table      │
 └──────────────┬────────────────┘
                ↓
 ┌───────────────────────────────┐
 │ Record in Maintenance_History │
 └──────────────┬────────────────┘
                ↓
 ┌───────────────────────────────┐
 │ BI Reports / Alerts           │
 └───────────────────────────────┘
                ↓
          ┌──────────────┐
          │     END      │
          └──────────────┘
